caissify-pairings — FIDE Dutch System Pairing Engine
Copyright 2026 Alexis Vargas

This product includes caissify-pairings
(https://github.com/lexisvar/caissify_pairings), a FIDE A.7-conformant
Swiss pairing engine implementing the FIDE Dutch System (C.04.3),
Free Pairings Checker (C.04.A §A.4), and Random Tournament Generator
(C.04.A §A.5).

